### ========================================
### MECHA SOFT API - TESTES COMPLETOS
### ========================================
### Base URL: http://localhost:5039
### Swagger UI: http://localhost:5039/swagger

### ========================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO E CONTAS
### ========================================

### POST /api/accounts/register - Registrar Novo Usuário (Cliente)
POST http://localhost:5039/api/accounts/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "joao_silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "role": 1
}

### POST /api/accounts/register - Registrar Funcionário
POST http://localhost:5039/api/accounts/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_user",
  "email": "admin@mechasoft.pt",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "role": 2
}

### POST /api/accounts/login - Login
POST http://localhost:5039/api/accounts/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "joao_silva",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### GET /api/accounts/users - Listar Usuários
GET http://localhost:5039/api/accounts/users?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

