### ========================================
### 7. ORDENS DE SERVIÇO
### ========================================

### POST /api/service-orders - Criar Ordem de Serviço
POST http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "vehicleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "description": "Manutenção completa do veículo - mudança de óleo e inspeção",
  "priority": 1,
  "estimatedCost": 150.00,
  "estimatedDelivery": "2024-12-15T16:00:00Z",
  "mechanicId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
  "requiresInspection": true,
  "internalNotes": "Cliente preferencial - prioridade alta"
}

### POST /api/service-orders - Criar Ordem de Serviço 2
POST http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "vehicleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
  "description": "Reparação de travões - ruído anormal",
  "priority": 2,
  "estimatedCost": 200.00,
  "estimatedDelivery": "2024-12-16T14:00:00Z",
  "mechanicId": null,
  "requiresInspection": false,
  "internalNotes": "Verificar sistema de travagem completo"
}

### GET /api/service-orders - Listar Ordens de Serviço
GET http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### GET /api/service-orders/{id} - Obter Ordem por ID
GET http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007

### PUT /api/service-orders/{id}/status - Atualizar Status
PUT http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2,
  "notes": "Iniciada reparação - peças encomendadas"
}

### PUT /api/service-orders/{id}/mechanic - Atribuir Mecânico
PUT http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008/mechanic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mechanicId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
}

### POST /api/service-orders/{id}/services - Adicionar Serviço à Ordem
POST http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000009",
  "quantity": 1,
  "estimatedHours": 1.5,
  "discountPercentage": 10.0,
  "mechanicId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
}

### POST /api/service-orders/{id}/parts - Adicionar Peça à Ordem
POST http://localhost:5039/api/service-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007/parts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006",
  "quantity": 2,
  "discountPercentage": 5.0
}

